13 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
14 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
15 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 4019.1 of Title 69, unless there
16 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
17 A. The Oklahoma Department of Transportation shall require a
18 post-installation inspection for any storm pipe that does not pass a
19 structural dead load test prior to installation.
20 B. The post-installation inspection shall be conducted by a
21 qualified engineer or inspector approved by the Department to ensure
22 compliance with industry standards, including, but not limited to:
23 1. Structural integrity under expected loads;
24 2. Proper bedding and backfill placement;
